    "offline-message-com-apple-Mail-help" : {
      "navigation" : "false",
      "content" : "<div id='offline-message-com-apple-Mail-help' class='apd-topic'><div class='subjectids'><a name='offline-message-com-apple-Mail-help'><\/a><\/div><h1 class='title topictitle1'>目前無法取得所選的主題<\/h1><div class='body conbody'><p class='p'>請確定您已經連接 Internet。如需連線的相關協助，請選擇“蘋果”選單 >“系統偏好設定⋯”，按一下“網路”，然後按一下“協助我⋯”。<\/p><p class='p'>若您已經連接 Internet 但仍無法顯示內容，請稍後再試一次。<\/p><\/div><\/div>",
      "alternativeName" : "目前無法取得所選的主題",
      "name" : "目前無法取得所選的主題",
      "class" : "content-not-available-message"
    },
    "cpmlwn" : {
      "navigation" : "false",
      "content" : "<div id='cpmlwn' class='apd-topic'><div class='subjectids'><a name='cpmlwn'><\/a><a name='almail38576'><\/a><a name='almail38577'><\/a><\/div><h1 class='title topictitle1'><img class='image category-art' src='..\/media\/xicnml.png' height='32' width='32'>Mail 的新功能<\/h1><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>OS X Mountain Lion 中的 Mail 提供許多重大的新功能，讓您輕鬆的傳送、接收及檢視郵件。<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class='topic task nested1' id='cpmlwn-a'><a name='cpmlwn-a'><!-- --><\/a><h2 class='title topictitle2'>VIP<\/h2><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>將寄件人標示為 VIP，以追蹤來自重要人員的郵件。從您收到的郵件中，其名稱旁邊若顯示星號，即表示該寄件人是您的 VIP。Mail 會在“喜好項目”列上為每一位 VIP 加入信箱，以便接收來自 VIP 的郵件。<\/p><p class='p'><a class='xref unresolved-reference' href='#mail40589'>將寄件人標示為 VIP<\/a><\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class='topic task nested1' id='cpmlwn-c'><a name='cpmlwn-c'><!-- --><\/a><h2 class='title topictitle2'>新郵件的通知<\/h2><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>您可以在 Mail 偏好設定中設定選項，依據收取郵件的信箱或寄件人來顯示通知。<\/p><p class='p'><a class='xref unresolved-reference' href='#mail40585'>自定何時顯示電子郵件通知<\/a><\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class='topic task nested1' id='cpmlwn-e'><a name='cpmlwn-e'><!-- --><\/a><h2 class='title topictitle2'>以不同格式共享網頁<\/h2><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>當您共享 Safari 的網頁時，您可以選擇傳送的格式。例如，您可以用連結或 PDF 的方式來傳送網頁。<\/p><p class='p'><a class='xref unresolved-reference' href='#mail40723'>傳送從 Safari 共享的網頁<\/a><\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class='related-links'><div class='linklist linklist'><strong>相關主題<\/strong><br><div><a class='link unresolved-reference' href='#mail35803'>收發所有帳號的電子郵件<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>",
      "alternativeName" : "Mail 的新功能",
      "name" : "Mail 的新功能",
      "summary" : "了解 Mail 中的新功能。"
    },
    "searchable-landing-com-apple-Mail-help" : {
      "navigation" : "false",
      "content" : "<div class='apd-topic' id='searchable-landing-com-apple-Mail-help'><div class='subjectids'><a name='searchable-landing-com-apple-Mail-help'><\/a><\/div><h1 class='title topictitle1'>Mail 輔助說明<\/h1><div class='body conbody'><div class='section'><h2 class='title sectiontitle'>Mail 輔助說明<\/h2><p class='p'>可搜尋的主題<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>",
      "alternativeName" : "Mail 輔助說明",
      "name" : "Mail 輔助說明",
